description.content:
Located in Bacolod, 1.5 km from Negros Museum, OYO 543 Negrense Suites provides accommodation with a restaurant, free private parking, a bar and a shared lounge. With free WiFi, this 2-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and room service.

Panaad Stadium is 6 km from the hotel, while Mambukal Zipline is 27 km away. The nearest airport is New Bacolod-Silay Airport, 3.6 km from OYO 543 Negrense Suites.

OYO 517 Jcad Hotel Lahug features air-conditioned rooms with cable flat-screen TV in the Lahug district of Cebu City. This 2-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and room service. SM City Cebu is 3 km from the hotel and Fuente Osmena Circle is 4 km away.

With a private bathroom equipped with a bidet and free toiletries, rooms at the hotel also have a city view.

Situated conveniently in the Quezon City district of Manila, OYO 430 Michael's Place is set 13 km from Smart Araneta Coliseum, 17 km from Malacanang Palace and 17 km from SM Megamall. With a restaurant, the 2-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. Rizal Park is 19 km from the hotel and Power Plant Mall is 21 km away.

At the hotel, all rooms come with a desk and a flat-screen TV.

Languages spoken at the 24-hour front desk include Filipino and English.

All units are equipped with air conditioning, TV with cable channels, refrigerator, coffee maker, shower, hairdryer and work desk. All rooms at the hotel are equipped with a wardrobe and a private bathroom.

The staff at the 24-hour reception speaks Spanish and French, and is always on hand to help.

Due to the current travel environment, and as part of local prevention efforts, this hotel has temporarily suspended operations. Madrid-Barajas Airport is less than 10 minutes away via shuttle and Madrid city center is 20 km from our door. Daily hot breakfast and WiFi are free, and our seasonal outdoor pool is open June  September.

It only takes 2 minutes to walk from the hotel to My Khe beach, 5km to the airport, 3km to Han Market.
